{
  "stem": "1680.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 66.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we came to America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In France, it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived-- three daughters were born in France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had a manufacturer from shirts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing is, first of all, Margot wanted to be with her family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have any family in France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And secondly, at that time was a little dangerous that French will become Communist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- I-- somebody by the name Thorez, Maurice Thorez.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was-- he wanted to run for Prime Minister, and he was a Communist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was, at that time, was a little dangerous, this, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we decided to leave when we could leave for America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we give up this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in France, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a manufacturing from shirts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started-- we have to do something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we started out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We bought materials and we opened up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our-- our name was-- I still have paper is I can show.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you're interested, I can show you-- the papers, that is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] it was called-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the manufacture from shirts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had women working for us sewing these shirts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had sales.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a partner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then by then, we separated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had ourselves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after we got the visas, so we liquidated everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we sold our apartment, and we left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife, my brother, and I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother left three months earlier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, we have-- there was another thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother-- you have to have an affidavit from America to-- somebody has to guarantee for you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he had an affidavit from an aunt, Margot's aunt, and also from her brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
